<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal">
<head>
<title>Macro one document</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>What this file is</h1>
  <p>Ths document exposes a single METAL macro that can be re-used by other METAL documents.</p>
  <p metal:define-macro="test">
    <span metal:define-slot="slot1">This is slot 1 from the macro</span>
    <span metal:define-slot="slot2">This is slot 2 from the macro</span>
    <span metal:define-slot="slot3">This is slot 3 from the macro</span>
  </p>
</body>
</html>